                     <interp inst="t18390617-1731-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp> for stealing, on the <rs id="t18390617-cd-14" type="crimeDate">
                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18390617-1731-offence-1 t18390617-cd-14"></join>24th of May</rs>, 1 handkerchief, value 2<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., the goods of Sir <persName id="t18390617-name-148" type="victimName">
